data.description: If you're an outdoor enthusiast, this is the home for you! Nestled in the sought after Setters Pointe neighborhood, this residence offers a lifestyle where nature and recreation are right at your doorstep. Explore the network of trails within the subdivision, leading to the Brighton State Recreation Areas nearly 5,000 acres as your extended backyard. Whether you love hiking, biking, or a leisurely stroll, these paths are your gateway to the great outdoors. Enjoy access to the community basketball court for friendly games and a picnic area for delightful outdoor gatherings. It's the perfect blend of community and recreation, just steps away from your front door. Imagine weekends spent at Bishop Lake beach, just minutes away! This home backs to woods, providing an extra layer of tranquility and privacy. The fire-pit area sets the stage for cozy evenings under the stars—an outdoor retreat right in your backyard. The 4-car side entry garage not only accommodates your vehicles but also offers ample storage space and includes a walk in mudroom. Partially finished basement with full bathroom and bar area is ready for your finishing touches. Brighton School District benefits with Hamburg Township taxes. With proximity to schools, shopping, and restaurants, every convenience is within reach. Quick access to freeways ensures that you're well-connected to the surrounding areas. Ready to embrace a lifestyle where outdoor adventures and modern comforts harmonize? Make 7622 SETTERS POINTE Drive your gateway to the great outdoors. Schedule a tour today and embrace a life where nature isn't just a destination; it's part of your everyday.
